{"tid":452200,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"不如講下大家用咩hair styling product","createTime":"2017-10-30T03:06:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T12:09:59.000Z","uid":47773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"027c4ffe3d56bbf4d89ac61812878d080fb92ba7","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:06:47.000Z","msg":"我以前用hanz de fuko，所有product都有用過除咗gel嗰支<br />\n但自從佢個cs on99唔撚覆人email之後，又唔知做乜鳩無啦啦開blumann波之後我就無再用<br />\n之後我有一排用中學雞gatsby 紫色嗰樽用咗好耐，近排轉咗用blumann Cavaliers clay，用落同hdf嗰個claymation其實無乜分別<br />\n但我搵唔返一個同quicksand差唔多嘅pre styling，大家一齊講下你哋用咩，有咩推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb920ea5b130fbb628c1978bc267661ab12c032","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T03:16:27.000Z","msg":"推下先"},{"pid":"28e067d884e2b85e44caefdcc107cf9f63443d56","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab32a0661070b7be330aaac0ed34c860001eba7","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33268d0e0ffa30d6ef68c11e63a931152369c6bf","tid":452200,"uid":36754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:32:14.000Z","msg":"唔中意quicksand 落完好kick 仲有盒用過既 有冇興趣？"},{"pid":"cfbc2da8ddc8c50e64bf33f37354e22c4aeb356a","tid":452200,"uid":35490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T04:38:13.000Z","msg":"pre styling 用aveda 隻 thickening tonic, 幾好用"},{"pid":"5d58f17715788dfb0f82a3a1e624ac38852ec349","tid":452200,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-1