img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13a53923cd34cbc1d531d9effe522976e76655ea","tid":452200,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:38:45.000Z","msg":"用緊Hanz De Fuko既quicksand同埋morris motley chrome<br />\npomade用緊Prospectors iron ore，隻味真係香到呀媽都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57e27e6dc51df7cb40a3aa5712307d98e9f18ae1","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用緊Hanz De Fuko既quicksand同埋morris motley chrome<br />\npomade用緊Prospectors iron ore，隻味真係香到呀媽都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nMorris motley 係咪真係好好用？<br />\n唔知點解啲pomade永遠都好香，hanz de fuko嗰個又係好鬼香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"532e19d7ccd7027b278924f57ea3f676593836de","tid":452200,"uid":67946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:40:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>bumble and bumble<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打邊到買 對佢支surf spray foam有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cf4b2df8bb2e965e894c93e4166e8b32869d3d","tid":452200,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:41:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用開blumaan smooth，濕頭髮落，吹乾就得好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前買左blumaan cavalier clay用左1,2次但唔啱用，樓主有冇興趣？</blockquote><br />\nBlumann smooth姐係邊隻？</blockquote><br />\n咪姐係佢起家果隻styling meraki<br />\n一開始出果隻係黑色盒，後尾出左隻藍色label寫住smooth，話係易推開易上頭無咁痴手喎，後來blumaan直頭phase out左隻黑色原版，直接將smooth取代佢"},{"pid":"f552d56e2530c77172b4c2d1588213b3fd11445a","tid":452200,"uid":88134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用緊Hanz De Fuko既quicksand同埋morris motley chrome<br />\npomade用緊Prospectors iron ore，隻味真係香到呀媽都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Morris motley 係咪真係好好用？</span><br />\n唔知點解啲pomade永遠都好香，hanz de fuko嗰個又係好鬼香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拿呢樣好難講<br />\n因為呢D野都係要夾髮型同髮質<br />\n我自己覺得都算好用，但係要用係傾向短既髮型例如quiff，d texture真係好出，亦都夠hold既，但係我早一排個髮型都仲係undercut既時候呢，可能係因為頭髮偏長，個效果唔係咁理想，hold唔得耐，可能我唔識掌握個份量啦，短髮用就真係好好<br />\n<br />\n另外我試過用quicksand打底，再落morris motley chrome同埋用係超市買到既mosse打底，再落chrome，我自己覺得後者感覺良好d，quicksand打底夠乾身，但好似唔夠企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc47f2f81811d16354ba2d362026addb8955994","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:55:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用開blumaan smooth，濕頭髮落，吹乾就得好方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前買左blumaan cavalier clay用左1,2次但唔啱用，樓主有冇興趣？</blockquote><br />\nBlumann smooth姐係邊隻？</blockquote><br />\n咪姐係佢起家果隻styling meraki<br />\n一開始出果隻係黑色盒，後尾出左隻藍色label寫住smooth，話係易推開易上頭無咁痴手喎，後來blumaan直頭phase out左隻黑色原版，直接將smooth取代佢</blockquote><br />\nblumann都話佢呢隻用嚟做pre styling 係無得頂，其實我一直想試下，但我又驚無佢自己講到咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c3c771e907b6f4b6e96589f1201af2ab123ddd","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T09:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用緊Hanz De Fuko既quicksand同埋morris motley chrome<br />\npomade用緊Prospectors iron ore，隻味真係香到呀媽都唔認得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Morris motley 係咪真係好好用？</span><br />\n唔知點解啲pomade永遠都好香，hanz de fuko嗰個又係好鬼香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n拿呢樣好難講<br />\n因為呢D野都係要夾髮型同髮質<br />\n我自己覺得都算好用，但係要用係傾向短既髮型例如quiff，d texture真係好出，亦都夠hold既，但係我早一排個髮型都仲係undercut既時候呢，可能係因為頭髮偏長，個效果唔係咁理想，hold唔得耐，可能我唔識掌握個份量啦，短髮用就真係好好<br />\n<br />\n另外我試過用quicksand打底，再落morris motley chrome同埋用係超市買到既mosse打底，再落chrome，我自己覺得後者感覺良好d，quicksand打底夠乾身，但好似唔夠企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但quicksand正就正在佢抽佢你本身濕髮嗰陣打底嗰啲水份，等你快啲吹乾同易吹啲<br />\n同埋我有一排頭髮好短就咁用佢做型都夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"997031bb5e08f31c236339927b38225dfe6122e3","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T18:55:17.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"7cdaa89aca0c49429281360218cbb39caf916deb","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T03:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dad297554fe9d535151b585ed296e729a2a3fb2","tid":452200,"uid":35490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T05:03:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>pre styling 用aveda 隻 thickening tonic, 幾好用</blockquote><br />\n邊度有得買？</blockquote><br />\nsorry 我都唔知香港邊到有"},{"pid":"7713fa74ae146b19f2defc49d6b8e8214bf2e58b","tid":452200,"uid":47773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T11:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>pre styling 用aveda 隻 thickening tonic, 幾好用</blockquote><br />\n邊度有得買？</blockquote><br />\nsorry 我都唔知香港邊到有</blockquote><br />\n唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b88f5c34b03de7214785759cbbafb81357021df","tid":452200,"uid":1740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T15:13:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}